    <!-- Slide 5: Drag fields -->
    <section class="slide">
      <h2>4. Step 3 – Drag Fields into the PivotTable</h2>
      <div class="layout-two-col">
        <div>
          <p>We’ll build a summary like:</p>
          <p><strong>“Total/average Amount for each Category”</strong></p>
          <p>Drag fields in the PivotTable Fields pane:</p>
          <p>
            <span class="tag">Category → Rows</span>
            <span class="tag">Amount → Values</span>
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>Drag your <strong>Category</strong> field (e.g., Subject, Product) to <strong>Rows</strong>.</li>
            <li>Drag your numeric field (e.g., Amount, Score) to <strong>Values</strong>.</li>
          </ol>
          <p>To change from Sum to Average:</p>
          <ol start="3">
            <li>Click the small arrow on <em>Sum of Amount</em> (or similar) in the Values box.</li>
            <li>Choose <strong>Value Field Settings…</strong>.</li>
            <li>Select <strong>Average</strong> → <strong>OK</strong>.</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="box">
            Now your PivotTable answers:
            <em>“For each Category, what is the total/average Amount?”</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="image-frame">
            <!-- PivotTable layout illustration -->
            <svg viewBox="0 0 260 150" aria-label="PivotTable layout and fields">
              <title>PivotTable layout and fields</title>
              <rect x="0" y="0" width="260" height="150" rx="10" fill="#020617" stroke="#1f2937"/>
              <!-- pivot area -->
              <rect x="10" y="15" width="140" height="120" rx="5" fill="#020617" stroke="#374151"/>
              <rect x="12" y="17" width="136" height="14" fill="#111827"/>
              <text x="16" y="27" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">Category</text>
              <!-- sample rows -->
              <text x="16" y="43" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">Category A</text>
              <text x="16" y="56" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">Category B</text>
              <text x="16" y="69" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">Category C</text>
              <text x="90" y="43" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">123.4</text>
              <text x="90" y="56" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">98.7</text>
              <text x="90" y="69" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">75.2</text>
              <!-- fields pane -->
              <rect x="160" y="15" width="90" height="120" rx="5" fill="#020617" stroke="#374151"/>
              <text x="165" y="25" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">PivotTable Fields</text>
              <!-- fields list -->
              <rect x="165" y="32" width="80" height="40" rx="3" fill="#020617" stroke="#374151"/>
              <text x="168" y="42" font-size="7" fill="#e5e7eb">☑ Date</text>
